Function to clean household data

Source: R/30-clean_hh.R
clean_hh.Rd

Function to clean household data

clean_hh(df, checks)

Arguments

df

A data.frame collected for the Myanmar MCCT Programme Evaluation Study containing household data. Default is hh.
checks

A data.frame containing check values for cleaning.

Value

A data.frame equivalent to df but with extraneous observations and other variables cleaned ready for further processing.

Examples

clean_hh(df = hh, checks = checks)
